readme:
# Purple Sky theme

Based around soft purples that please the eye. Made because I couldn't find something in the theme shop I liked.
It's really simple, but if you want to use it too, be my guest!

It goes best with my [Purple Sky Syntax](https://github.com/InValidFire/purple-sky-syntax)

![Purple Sky](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/364324213286371340/596037559558209537/unknown.png)
